{"id": 634, "genre": 1001, "title": "\b作为一个有点钱了的80后，你会买什么？", "description": "从校园到职场，从单身到小家庭，你的购物习惯发生了什么变化？（题图来自：Peter Oumanski for WSJ）", "record_count": 6580, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160703130126SHlzcXaFsy7gUIjk.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2015-11-16T10:56:45Z", "options": [{"id": 25496, "content": "买奶粉尿布", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 304975}, {"id": 25600, "content": "环球旅行和留学吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 54, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 203294}, {"id": 26368, "content": "投资自己学习，学完继续投资，实现财务自由后，做些更有意义的事情！", "image": "img/option/option/201606052116378jxMXHd9kwu6tI0s.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 313277}, {"id": 25601, "content": "肯定什么都买质量好的 不再注重便宜 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 291704}, {"id": 26625, "content": "买自己需要的东东", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 287877}, {"id": 25602, "content": "买块积家，买辆Ghibli", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 284187}, {"id": 25603, "content": "投资健康！", "image": null, "praise_count": 49, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 308112}, {"id": 26115, "content": "由量及质", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 202397}, {"id": 38915, "content": "我是90", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 403499}, {"id": 28164, "content": "给媳妇儿买包", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 299538}, {"id": 33029, "content": "衣服一洗一换，营养用餐，强身健体学咏春，长生不老终南山。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 347847}, {"id": 25609, "content": "终于敢进买手店了，终于可以不在国内零售店买东西了", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 113353}, {"id": 32266, "content": "立马投资自己，去开拓眼界去学习新东西。", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 343328}, {"id": 25611, "content": "车", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 284207}, {"id": 25613, "content": "除了房屋，汽车和一些奢侈品。似乎很难找到贵的买不起的东西，看心情，看品质。", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 308167}, {"id": 25615, "content": "应该不会有钱了", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 194834}, {"id": 28177, "content": "来自老去的90后:来赚更多的钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 285375}, {"id": 31249, "content": "依旧没钱??", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 334825}, {"id": 25618, "content": "根据市场做小点的投资把钱分成10分，2分投资，8分在银行里，等以后有什么急需要用的时候用。", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 308172}, {"id": 26130, "content": "享受生活吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 311162}, {"id": 25619, "content": "随心所欲的去旅行。", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 215356}, {"id": 25620, "content": "各种独立小众美好设计——90后", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 298619}, {"id": 25622, "content": "背包全球旅游", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 298216}, {"id": 26392, "content": "要务实，不要过多追求面子上的无用的奢侈品", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 313438}, {"id": 25625, "content": "千金不换我欣喜", "image": "img/option/option/20160702182612v4nbRHJ8OhAduF7j.jpeg", "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 308205}, {"id": 25626, "content": "千金不换我欣喜", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 308205}, {"id": 25627, "content": "开始享受小轻奢 埃及棉床品 温柔的香氛之类 好包好鞋也要投资", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 308204}, {"id": 26651, "content": "买生活，优质的生活", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 238704}, {"id": 25884, "content": "买衣服开始喜欢买简洁，经典款，更注重细节和材质，喜欢ACNE STUDIO, JCREW, CLUB MONACO.", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 310041}, {"id": 32797, "content": "买不起", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 346512}, {"id": 25630, "content": "旅行，给老婆买贵一点的化妆品终于不眨眼了。１ｋ左右的衣服终于敢下手了", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1504}, {"id": 26142, "content": "买能带来收益的资产", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 218185}, {"id": 26398, "content": "开个不为盈利只为乐意的店，例如花店、咖啡店或者书店～", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 313455}, {"id": 28447, "content": "学习理财让钱增值，减少等价的工作，多些时间提高生活品质，旅行，帮助其他人", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 324592}, {"id": 26144, "content": "当然是拔草！拔各种草！", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 311388}, {"id": 25634, "content": "去旅行 独自去旅行 淡季独自去旅行", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 295849}, {"id": 25891, "content": "想把自己买成90后", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 219212}, {"id": 26147, "content": "钱就没够过", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 246450}, {"id": 25636, "content": "买一堆死萌死萌的创意小玩意", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 305652}, {"id": 25637, "content": "听说房产权即将由70年变为永久。奈何没钱。", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 168505}, {"id": 26149, "content": "我会买保险，因为时代变化很快，都不知道以后钱还经花不?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 311419}, {"id": 26152, "content": "买又怪又傻的", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 307087}, {"id": 25642, "content": "秋田犬", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 240814}, {"id": 26154, "content": "有钱就买下天猫！天天双十一！", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 198636}, {"id": 25647, "content": "投资去培养新技能，多点技能不会吃亏。旅游长见识。", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 308448}, {"id": 31791, "content": "女人", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 340417}, {"id": 25904, "content": "我在做会梦", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 309808}, {"id": 28977, "content": "买90后的青春", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 328253}, {"id": 25650, "content": "真的有钱的话，就要所有产品都买一遍，比如说要买耳机，所有牌子的耳机都买一遍，然后挑出最好的那一样，把其它放到储物柜里，以后捐给博物馆。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 5}, {"id": 26162, "content": "漫画", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 235090}]}